          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The name <strong>Torto</strong> is inspired by the natural engineering of the tortoise shell—a lightweight yet incredibly strong barrier designed to withstand the elements and protect what’s inside.</p><p>Our mission is to provide North American homeowners with custom-engineered covers that offer:</p><ul><li><strong>Maximum Heat Retention:</strong> Reducing your energy bills even in the harshest winters.</li><li><strong>Total Customization:</strong> No two spas are exactly the same. We specialize in custom shapes, oversized swim spas, and unique configurations.</li><li><strong>Long-Lasting Performance:</strong> Using marine-grade materials and reinforced stitching to ensure your cover doesn’t just look good today, but performs for years to come.</li></ul>"
